name: Snoop Dogg Presents The Joker's Wild
original_name: Snoop Dogg Presents The Joker's Wild
overview: Snoop Dogg, who counted The Joker's Wild as his favorite game show growing up, will host TBS's new version, which is set in his casino, complete with a gigantic slot machine, as well as giant dice and playing cards. Streetwise questions and problem solving, not just book smarts, will rule the floor, with all the action controlled by the one and only Snoop D-O Double G.

episodes.name: The Game is On...Doggy Style
episodes.overview: Seth Rogen tells us what celeb he most wants to get high with. Snoop quizzes a pot farming party planner and a Pokemon master on names of pot strains and uses his superpowers to meld with their minds. The Winner spins for a chance at $25,000.

episodes.name: Wild Enough To Do It Doggystyle
episodes.overview: Kelly Osbourne shows us how to do it the "UK Way," Snoop channels his inner soul singer and hosts a new morning show with Regis Philbin, and gangsta knowledge is tested. A dental hygienist & football coach spin the wheels for a shot at $25,000.

episodes.name: What You Know Can Win Dough
episodes.overview: Supermodel Karlie Kloss brings the fashion facts, Michael Strahan busts a move, and Seth Rogen schools us on pots effects on our brains. A sommelier and a bartender take on the wheels to grab that $25,000.

episodes.name: The Cash Never Stops and the Knowledge Drops
episodes.overview: Snoop paints puzzling masterpieces, Wiz Khalifa and Snoop read Dr. Seuss books, and Snoop shows us why "black don't crack." A teacher and a brand ambassador go up against the wheel for a chance at $25,000.
